Title: Story of a Spectacular Victory
Description:
That was a majestic fight!

Elder Poa in Iskaara will be interested in listening to the story of that impressive victory.
ObjectivesText: Tell the story of your victory to Elder Poa in Iskaara.
CompletionText:
The most amazing stories might happen with anyone. Especially if one fearlessly ventures into an enemy lair...

Our deeds make us who we are, and I'm always eager to learn of the most impressive acts and make them inspiration to others.
RewardText:
Oh, you have a story for me? Sit down, let me hear it.

<Elder Poa listens to your tale of a victory over a peculiar foe.>

That was thrilling! Thank you for sharing that with me, young one. I will remember this tale!
